snippet.title: PRIMAA Youtube
snippet.description: The Peace Region Independent Media Arts Association is a non-profit society founded in 2013 to support and develop film and digital media artists throughout the Peace Region of Northern Alberta & BC. We exist to support and nurture original media artists and filmmakers of all kinds.
